external_knowledge:
- A 'lab technician' is a role that typically involves conducting experiments and collecting samples; 
- The term 'at least 11 samples' refers to the condition COUNT(s.sample_id) > 10; 
- 'total sensor value' refers to the sum of sensor values recorded by the sensor in a trial, calculated as SUM(s.sensor_value); 
- 'total samples' refers to the number of samples collected in a trial, calculated as COUNT(s.sample_id).
